{"tid":1312392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要做差佬？","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:34:22.000Z","uid":38705,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17040b49b479199e2c84ac6527874370bf67ff34","tid":1312392,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"點解要做差佬？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以揼你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？"},{"pid":"3f0ce3262bd8f8dbfb019310cbef31cfd09639ac","tid":1312392,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書唔做狗做得乜"}]}